i3wm Keybindings

For reference consult our WIKI:
https://discovery.endeavouros.com/window-tiling-managers/i3-wm/

ď…Ľ = windows key

# start xfce4-terminal
ď…Ľ+Return 

# kill focused window
ď…Ľ+q

# Application menu search by typing (fancy Rofi menu)
ď…Ľ+d

# fancy exit-menu on bottom right:
ď…Ľ+Shift+e

# lock the system
ď…Ľ+l

# reload the configuration file
ď…Ľ+Shift+c

# restart i3 inplace (preserves your layout/session, can be used to upgrade i3)
ď…Ľ+Shift+r

# keybinding in fancy rofi (automated)
F1

# change window focus
ď…Ľ+i focus up || ď…Ľ+Up
ď…Ľ+m focus down || ď…Ľ+Down
ď…Ľ+j focus left || ď…Ľ+Left
ď…Ľ+k focus right || ď…Ľ+Right

# switch workspace
ď…Ľ+Tab switch prev
ď…Ľ+w switch next

# move a focused window
ď…Ľ+Shift+j move left
ď…Ľ+Shift+k move down
ď…Ľ+Shift+b move up
ď…Ľ+Shift+o move right

# alternatively, you can use the cursor keys
ď…Ľ+Shift+Left move left
ď…Ľ+Shift+Down move down
ď…Ľ+Shift+Up move up
ď…Ľ+Shift+Right move right

# enter fullscreen mode for the focused container
ď…Ľ+f fullscreen toggle

# change container layout
ď…Ľ+e layout toggle split
ď…Ľ+s layout tabbed

# toggle tiling / floating
ď…Ľ+Shift+space floating toggle

# change focus between tiling / floating windows
ď…Ľ+space focus mode_toggle

# resize floating window
ď…Ľ+right mouse button

